  "text": "Proof (from [CITATION_1] ). Consider A, B 1 , B 2 \u2208 C with embeddings f i : A \u2192 B i (for i = 1, 2). By (JEP), there is E \u2208 C and embeddings g i : B i \u2192 E.",
